The paper discusses web authentication mechanisms and their resistance to mimicry attacks. This topic falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and cyber security (cs.CY). The paper also evaluates invisible techniques such as device fingerprinting and geolocation mechanisms, which are related to topics in systems and information theory (cs.SI), software engineering (cs.SE), and machine learning (cs.LG).
